27:48.630 --> 27:50.090
Sedangkan awak sekarang masih baru.

27:50.780 --> 27:52.020
Kalau awak teruskan macam ini,

27:52.020 --> 27:53.500
20 orang menonton pun

27:53.500 --> 27:55.330
